'''等靜壓凹陷'''是指地壳的大部分沉入[[软流圈|软流圈]]。这种下沉是由地球表面的重物造成的，例如大陆上形成[[冰川|冰川]]後冰川的重力造成[[地表|地表]]凹陷。在大陆冰川消退后，通常又会出现{{link-en|等靜壓反弹|Isostatic rebound}}<ref>{{citation | url = http://www.physicalgeography.net/physgeoglos/i.html | chapter = Glossary of Terms: I | title = Physical geography | last = Waugh | year = 2006 | accessdate = 2021-02-07 | archive-date = 2021-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210425160149/http://www.physicalgeography.net/physgeoglos/i.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

